ActControlled Drugs and Substances Act
SubjectOrder Amending Schedule III to the Controlled Drugs and Substances Act (BZP and TFMPP)
PrecisOrder Amending SCHEDULE III TO THE CONTROLLED DRUGS AND SUBSTANCES ACT (BZP AND TFMPP) in order to protect the health and safety of Canadians by reducing the availability of two piperazine derivatives in Canada by listing the substances in Schedule III of the Controlled Drugs and Substances Act.
